Bunch of short Quake defrag maps by Chronos in one map.

Stage 1: [chronos-bardok](https://ws.q3df.org/map/chronos-bardok/)

Stage 2: [cpm_3](http://ws.q3df.org/map/cpm_3/)

Stage 3: [dfwc02-4](https://ws.q3df.org/map/dfwc02-4/)

Stage 4: [cpm_6](https://ws.q3df.org/map/cpm_6/)

Stage 5: [cpm_5](https://ws.q3df.org/map/cpm_5/)

Bonus: [vanilla_09](https://ws.q3df.org/map/vanilla_09/)

Map is about 1 min long if nofailed

Possible on scroll and 400 vel cap
